race.description: Share Bets With Tabtouch Bet Loop Handicap
race.comment: THE CALABRESE (4) had plenty of support in the Batavia Sprint at Geraldton last time out following a strong win here the start prior. Back to 1000m is probably the niggle, but he rates highly on his recent efforts. Maps to be closer to the speed and looks poised to strike. MAGNIQUE (3) won fresh before leading them up last week over 1200m and she was only reeled in by a smart one. The wide draw is a query, but with her early speed and a touch of luck she can offset the draw. At her peak third-up now and can go one better. LAST STYLEBENDER (13) has just missed in both runs this time in, knocking on the door in a CL1 most recently. The inside draw is ideal as he'll be right on the speed from an inside barrier and a bold showing is expected. OVERDRIVE (12) bolted up here last start when beating LAST STYLEBENDER and that form reads well for this. LUCKY I AM (8) has trialled well coming in and can be in this for a long way from a good draw.
